{"tid":2089594,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"敬各黃店員工，工作期間如非必要，請勿回答其他問題。","createTime":"2020-07-01T18:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T14:58:15.000Z","uid":219007,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8c5e7c58ad1bd830a4a306fffdd34aefeebb10","tid":2089594,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"呢條法例就係為咗震懾嚇人，所以短期之內一定會做啲好出位嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往一年經驗，佢哋好可能利用便衣去你哋舖頭食飯，同你地傾吓計套下料，甚至引導你認同某啲言論，一旦中招可能會掃你場，再上新聞大做文章嚇人。根據法例條文講法，食客都可以屬於支援角色，如果佢進取啲，到時真係即時冚店剷。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋肯定一早有哂成條黃店list，諗住搣紙已經走唔甩。所以而家唯一嘅方法總之就係喺工作期間，所有員工如非必要外，例如工作需要等，唔好回答多餘問題，唔好俾佢氹自己踩！ 有人同你傾偈要小心，後果可以好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以當我散播恐懼，但而家現實係要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲嘢佢哋唔係做唔出，便衣冼人過往成日出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋咁做係合乎佢地常理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係非常時期，全世界自己小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6aacecccaef04538ec38f670e66380a658e5b6d","tid":2089594,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99264b1ba8c61c45a63aba15087f6a438d1a913a","tid":2089594,"uid":326195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:05:37.000Z","msg":"小心小心小小心"},{"pid":"bc50a6ee461dce1a76bd1f436aa4e7f980654017","tid":2089594,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算自我閹割，恐懼管理成功"},{"pid":"12964ad34aa00ed0a2b0bdd28e444835249ddbfd","tid":2089594,"uid":172223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52eHERX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52eHERX.png&h=1efd60ae&s={SIZE}\" />"}